00:22:06.200 --> 00:22:07.760
In the end, there's one tribulation short.

00:22:08.240 --> 00:22:09.360
They were on the giant turtle's back

00:22:09.360 --> 00:22:10.280
when it flipped over.

00:22:10.280 --> 00:22:11.320
All the scriptures fell in the water.

00:22:11.320 --> 00:22:12.000
They scrambled to

00:22:12.000 --> 00:22:13.800
fish them out and dried them

00:22:13.800 --> 00:22:14.520
on rocks.

00:22:15.280 --> 00:22:16.040
When they turned the pages,

00:22:16.720 --> 00:22:17.440
a corner went missing.

00:22:18.480 --> 00:22:20.240
Even Tang Sangzang was a little upset.

00:22:20.240 --> 00:22:22.200
But Sun Wukong,

00:22:23.160 --> 00:22:25.000
the Victorious Fighting Buddha,

00:22:25.760 --> 00:22:27.720
said nothing in this world

00:22:27.720 --> 00:22:29.280
is ever truly perfect.

