00:22:32.360 --> 00:22:34.600
So what are you worried about?

00:22:36.160 --> 00:22:37.480
Buddha must have

00:22:37.760 --> 00:22:39.560
known that Yudong

00:22:39.560 --> 00:22:40.400
and Daoqi

00:22:41.560 --> 00:22:42.280
are

00:22:43.560 --> 00:22:44.400
about

00:22:45.680 --> 00:22:46.600
