00:33:30.080 --> 00:33:31.400
and sent so many messages.

00:33:31.400 --> 00:33:32.320
No answer.

00:33:33.720 --> 00:33:34.840
I was so worried

00:33:34.840 --> 00:33:35.720
about him,

00:33:35.720 --> 00:33:36.360
and then

00:33:39.280 --> 00:33:40.080
I called

00:33:41.040 --> 00:33:42.440
his office.

