I heard his voice,

00:33:52.200 --> 00:33:52.880
and I

00:33:53.080 --> 00:33:54.040
felt so relieved.

00:33:54.040 --> 00:33:55.160
I asked him

00:33:55.160 --> 00:33:56.480
if he'd seen the news.

00:33:57.840 --> 00:33:59.040
He said yes.

00:33:59.800 --> 00:34:00.840
He said it was fine.

00:34:02.360 --> 00:34:03.400
I told him

00:34:03.400 --> 00:34:06.160
it had nothing to do with him.

00:34:06.160 --> 00:34:07.560
It was a black swan event,

00:34:09.400 --> 00:34:11.000
and he shouldn't overthink it.

00:34:14.880 --> 00:34:16.320
Then he said the same thing

00:34:16.480 --> 00:34:17.520
he told me

00:34:17.800 --> 00:34:18.880
when we first met.

00:34:19.080 --> 00:34:21.400
What seems like the end of the world today

00:34:21.639 --> 00:34:23.480
will be just a joke in ten years.

00:34:28.880 --> 00:34:29.760
He said

00:34:29.760 --> 00:34:30.560
the same words

00:34:30.560 --> 00:34:31.920
when we first met.

00:34:33.679 --> 00:34:35.400
I've never forgotten that.

